      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : «مِنْ شَرَفِ اَلرَّجُلِ أَنْ يُطَيِّبَ زَادَهُ إِذَا خَرَجَ فِي سَفَرٍ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2454 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings of Allah (swt) be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Part of a man's dignity is that he makes his provisions pleasant when he sets out on a journey.\""
        ]
      }
